            <title>[HBASE-16565] Add metrics for backup / restore</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-16565</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Exposing metrics for backup / restore would give admin insight on the overall operations.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The metrics should include (but are not limited to):&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;number of backups performed (full / incremental)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;number of restore&apos;s performed (full / incremental)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;number of aborted backups&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;number of aborted restore&apos;s&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;duration of backups performed&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;duration of restores performed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
